                    <img src="images/web_service.jpg" style="margin:5px;" alt="panacia softwares, website designing, website development, website designing and development in kanpur india " />
                    <div style="width:314px;margin:5px auto; text-align:justify" align="center">
                        <p>If you're serious about making your business succeed, you need a website. We can help you create an innovative, high quality, custom website that conveys your brand and business objective in a manner tailored for your target audience. Our web services encompasses of designing, redesigning, custom designing and development of website.</p>
