                    <div style="width:314px;margin:5px auto; text-align:justify" align="center">
                        <p>Panacia Softwares is a complete IT solution provider for your business. More than web and software development services, we also provides Third Party Services like payment gateway integration, SEO Implementation, Database Development services. Understanding the requirements of clients, we also offer the best possible domain & hosting service.</p>
